Key Match Events: The Denver Nuggets defeated the LA Clippers, tying the season series at two games a piece.
Russell Westbrook finished with 19 points, eight assists, and six rebounds.
Westbrook's rebound off a missed free throw by DeAndre Jordan went viral on social media.
Post-Match Reflections: Westbrook explained his viral moment, stating he told Ivica Zubac he would get the rebound if DeAndre Jordan missed the free throw.
Nuggets head coach Michael Malone commented on Westbrook's extra effort against his former team, but Westbrook said that is just how he plays every night.
